english:
No, nothing certain.
But even a Greater {Demon}
couldn't fell a {Priest Dragon}.\p{Booj}
Still, I'd like to go check.

...Mm, permission granted.
But be careful out there.\p{Granny}
Tell the Kapai

A {Priest Dragon} this size...
Likely Bardal, the Green Dragon
of the southern continent.\p{Booj}
Only by reputation, but Bardal
is gentle, a {Priest Dragon}
revered like Lord Frost.

Luke must be waiting for me
in that cold, cold mine.\p{CAROL}
Luke isn't stone... he can't
be... he can't...\p{CAROL}
Hic, hic...
Waaaaaaaaaaaah!

That's why I must go.
While other nations fight for
{SERUSH}, I, their princess,
cannot stay safe and idle.\p{CECILIA}
Please, send me to {SERUSH}{...}

{BOOJ}
Exactly.
It latches on as a larva, but the
best it manages is an ogre or {CHIMERA}
.
\p{BOOJ}
I've never heard of one feeding on
a dragon guarded by such strong
magic.

{WARRICK}
What do we do, {BOOJ}?
It just emerged, so its body
doesn't seem to move freely yet.
\p{WARRICK}
Should we kill it here and now?

...Gufah!?
To wound this {BIAGAN}
in single combat...\p{BIAGAN}
...Breis, was it?
I will never forget your name
so long as I live.

Great {MAGE} {BERG}
Weak, weak, weak, so weak.
And you call that a magic cannon?
Let me show you true {DARK MAGIC}.
GREAT {MAGE} {BERG}
{...}{O POPE OF THE HEAVENS},
{O POPE OF THE EARTH.}
Grant me, master of magic's law,
your power.
WITH The Flame At Evil'S Root,
BURN My Foes To Ash.
GREAT {MAGE} {BERG}
...Hades Magic Cannon.

Princess {CECILIA}
See this battle as the first step
to restoring {SERUSH KINGDOM}.
I'll allow no reckless valor,
no dog's death.\pPrincess {CECILIA}
For the King and all who died,
crush the demon army and bring
peaceful {SERUSH} back to us.\pPrincess {CECILIA}
...May the gods protect you.

Behold the might of the {BACCHUS II}
as a warship.\p {CAPTAIN ZERO}
{POP}!
Don't miss the slightest shift
in the spirits.

{・LET'S TALK.}
{・SELL ITEMS.}
{・TELEPORT.}
・Leave The {SHOP}.

{ZERO}
On the hill north of town grows a
crystal called the {CRYSTAL HORN}.
With it, we can defeat him.\p{ZERO}
Its magic seals his power, and we
can fight him as equals.

{ZERO}
If we can lure it out to the open,
the {BACCHUS II}'s ram can strike it.
Then I'll force a battle on the sand.\p{ZERO}
Can you manage it?

Spirit signal, abnormally active!\p{POP}
Range 1000, depth 80.\p{POP}
Range 800, depth 50.\p{POP}
Range 400, depth 30.\p{POP}
Range 100, depth 10.\p{POP}
Dead ahead, surfaciiing!

{PASHA}
Yes. Now that a mage has joined us,
it can be done.\p{PASHA}
Princess {CECILIA}.
...Give the word.

{PASHA}
The enemy has cast a huge
{MAGIC CIRCLE}
in the castle's underground
cathedral,
and moves through it.\p{PASHA}
{WARRICK} and the others will destroy
that {MAGIC CIRCLE}.

{CECILIA}
I forbid it, Master.
To die... I absolutely forbid it.
\p{CECILIA}
...I forbid it.
Your eyes... open your eyes.

{CECILIA}
...Watch me, {BREI}.
I will rebuild {SERUSH}.
\p{CECILIA}
A land more peaceful and richer
than any other, I will make it.
\p{CECILIA}
I swear it to all who died here.
